Package: scim-wijesekera
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, scim (<< 1.5.0)
Suggests: skim
Description: SCIM IMEngine Module for the Sinhala Wijesekera keyboard
 SCIM (Smart Common Input Method) is an input method (IM) platform.
 This module attempts to implement the keyboard layout described in 
 the "Sri Lanka Standard 1134:2004" document.
